Package: bun
Version: 1.3.14
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: curl, unzip, clang, glibc
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://bun.sh
Description: Incredibly fast JavaScript runtime (glibc wrapper for Termux)
 Bun is an all‑in‑one JavaScript/TypeScript toolkit. This package
 downloads the official Linux ARM64 or x86_64 binary and runs it
 inside the Termux glibc environment.
